trend_summary: Central township edges expand slowly along main roads, while surrounding farmland remains dominant. New industrial clusters emerge near the eastern river crossing, and scattered housing infill appears southward. Northern uplands show gradual reforestation. Overall change is modest, keeping the landscape predominantly rural with low built-up intensity.
